extendedInfo.description: FOR MEMBERS ONLY: The GE Money Rewards Program gives you access to a fantastic range of exclusive benefits and services at a fraction of the cost. As a member, you can look forward to discounts of up to 35% on clothing, health and beauty products and services, jewellery, furniture, dining, groceries and much more.Download the GE Money Rewards app on your mobile phone and redeem instant discounts on major brands and retail stores by simply presenting your digital member card before making your purchase.
